<li>Forde, Steven, <i>The ambition to rule&#160;: Alcibiades and the politics of imperialism in Thucydides</i>. Ithaca&#160;: Cornell University Press (1989). <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0801421381" class="internal">ISBN 0-8014-2138-1</a>.</li>
<li>Hanson, Victor Davis, <i>A War Like No Other: How the Athenians and Spartans Fought the Peloponnesian War</i>. New York: Random House (2005). <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1400060958" class="internal">ISBN 1-4000-6095-8</a>.</li>
<li>Hornblower, Simon, <i>A Commentary on Thucydides</i>. 2 vols. Oxford: Clarendon (1991-1996). <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0198150997" class="internal">ISBN 0-19-815099-7</a> (vol. 1), <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0199276250" class="internal">ISBN 0-19-927625-0</a> (vol. 2).</li>
